                "@type": "Question",
                "name": "What is BMI?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                    "@type": "Answer",
                    "text": "BMI (Body Mass Index) is a measurement that uses your height and weight to work out if your weight is healthy. It's calculated by dividing your weight in kilograms by your height in meters squared."
