                "@type": "Question",
                "name": "What are the BMI categories?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                    "@type": "Answer",
                    "text": "BMI categories are: Underweight (below 18.5), Normal weight (18.5-24.9), Overweight (25-29.9), and Obese (30 and above)."
